overview.en: GEC (GeneCoin) is a token mining pool project of the Lodecoin platform. As a connection medium, it integrates token exchange, platform functions, industrial functions, and user communities to forming a new industrial circle using tokens
overview.zh: GEC(GeneCoin) 是 Lodecoin 生态中最重要的矿池机制生态系统项目，以投入计算产出GEC通証。GEC作为连接媒介，将通证交换、平台功能、产业功能、⽤户社区融为⼀体，形成全新的运用通证的产业生态圈。
